          "reviewBody": "I am writing this review to tell the school to change the dispersal system , the dispersal system causes alot of traffic jams and it is a hassle for the parents. I will not change this review until the school does something about it's dispersal system. I have no problem with the academics of this school , the academics department is quite good but the dispersal system is one of the worst I've seen in any school .",
