            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very Bad Admission Process..!! I Faced Very Bad Experience Regarding This School Sometimes They Say Something And Sometimes They Say Something They Testing The Student During Admission Process Deeply Same Likes A Doctor Testing A Patient Deeply  I Think There's A Issue Of Donation So As Per My Knowledge This Sounds Not Good By School And I Faced Really Bad Experience About School .. Also They Try To Makes Pressure On Parents By Saying Student Not Doing Good During Admission Process Even Student Was Doing Good As Per My Knowledge It's Better To Go Other School Options.",
          "publisher": {
