            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We are really happy that we chose JBM school for our daughter. The school focus is on the overall development of the child, I’m glad that my daughter is getting equal opportunity to explore academics, sports and co-curicular activities. A special mention for all the pre primary teachers. We can see the efforts & hard work they put on a child for his/her development. I must say that the  school has one of the best teachers in pre primary. Keep doing good work.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
