            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have seen first school whose receptionist  is encouraging that parents are mandate to speak English with their kids. I went with my 2.5 year son to enquire about school  , my son spoke our national flag in hindi and the receptionist  was like we encourage parents to speak English.\nThis is shame , where our prime minister is giving world speech in hindi but school is encouraging  English as a medium. I saw photos of Kapil dev , wrestler sushil kumar, ram dev I am not sure whether all these people are fluent in English .\nI feel values should be above language.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
